scene: Start

You stand at the edge of a dark forest. The trees are tall and old.
There is only one way out. You must take it, but it may not go anywhere.

Choices:
- Go the only way you can -> Nowheresville

 ---

scene: Deep Woods

The forest closes around you. Something moves in the branches above.
You hear a low growl to your left and see a glimmer of light to your right.

Choices:
- Move toward the growl -> Wolf Encounter
- Move toward the light -> Mysterious Light
- Run back the way you came -> Start

---

scene: Village Square

The village is warm and safe. Your adventure ends here — for now.

THE END

---

scene: Wolf Encounter

You step toward the growl. A large wolf blocks the path, eyes glowing.
There is nowhere left to run.

THE END

---

scene: Mysterious Light

A lantern hangs from a branch, left by someone in a hurry.
You take it. The forest feels a little less frightening now.

Choices:
- Press deeper into the forest -> Deep Woods
- Head back toward the village -> Village Square
